org.codice.ddf.spatial.ogc.csw.catalog.common.converter

Class DefaultCswRecordMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codice.ddf.spatial.ogc.csw.catalog.common.converter.DefaultCswRecordMap

  • public class DefaultCswRecordMap
extends Object
    DefaultCswRecordMap defines the system map between CSW Records and a framework Metacard. It provides functions to retrieve the mapped values in either direction, and to retrieve metacard fields for a CSW field as a QName or just a local name as a String. If a mapped value isn't found, then the input value is used as the mapped value.
